{"tid":1135253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 震撼帳單」無上限港男驚被電訊商催交129萬　事主失眠：我驚要破產","createTime":"2019-05-02T07:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T02:52:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":189,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"40d5979c4fcf122a7a55b4d8fe05e1c75ae6d304","tid":1135253,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"一名1010手機用戶，早前收到一張帳單，指他欠款超過129萬元，因未能自動轉帳，促用戶盡早繳費。事主直言帳單的金額實在太大，更摸不著頭腦為何會欠逾百萬元巨款，收到後一度失眠，百思不得其解，更擔心是否會破產。<br />\n<br />\n事主陳先生接受TOPick訪問稱，自己是1010的老客戶，使用其電訊服務逾廿年，過去沒有申請自動轉帳服務，登記地址在舊居，4月尾其弟弟將1010發出的信件交予他，但當他見到信件內指他欠費達129.34萬元，即時嚇傻眼：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2340259/「震撼帳單」無上限港男驚被電訊商催交129萬%E3%80%80事主失眠：我驚要破產%E3%80%80?mtc=10001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2340259%2F%E3%80%8C%E9%9C%87%E6%92%BC%E5%B8%B3%E5%96%AE%E3%80%8D%E7%84%A1%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%90%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B7%E9%A9%9A%E8%A2%AB%E9%9B%BB%E8%A8%8A%E5%95%86%E5%82%AC%E4%BA%A4129%E8%90%AC%25E3%2580%2580%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E5%A4%B1%E7%9C%A0%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E9%A9%9A%E8%A6%81%E7%A0%B4%E7%94%A2%25E3%2580%2580%3Fmtc%3D10001&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu9qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=31c223e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2340259/「震撼帳單」無上限港男驚被電訊商催交129萬%E3%80%80事主失眠：我驚要破產%E3%80%80?mtc=10001</a>"},{"pid":"2482d7b8805153843850d36ecdeb242844de52ce","tid":1135253,"uid":19454,"like":134,"dislike":2,"score":132,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2340000/2340259/bill_thumb_20190502_E_V3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2340000%2F2340259%2Fbill_thumb_20190502_E_V3_600.jpg&h=e0d9597f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8df6cf71ff7841f3dfb91e067ed14b3997eb7d6a","tid":1135253,"uid":19454,"like":162,"dislike":4,"score":158,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:51:29.000Z","msg":"通訊事務管理局辦公室資料顯示，「帳單震撼」通常是由於用戶不經意或不自覺地使用了流動數據服務所致。為防止帳單震撼，流動營辦商已採取各種措施包括：<br />\n<br />\n容許用戶選擇取消個別服務；<br />\n設立收費上限；<br />\n為各類根據用量收費的流動服務設立用量上限；<br />\n以及向用量達到預定水平的客戶發出提示短訊。"},{"pid":"f6552651e9948fdb9252ad4298da0d0eadc038a4","tid":1135253,"uid":152516,"like":855,"dislike":2,"score":853,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:51:32.000Z","msg":"會俾錢先係難以置信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa24dab3671ec40a76f6cafd18f8ad2b3a1e7272","tid":1135253,"uid":102078,"like":690,"dislike":2,"score":688,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:53:02.000Z","msg":"佢個反應竟然係驚會破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16e060fa1eca8882c547e2f61f914f146853667","tid":1135253,"uid":23087,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:53:15.000Z","msg":"可以告佢?"},{"pid":"2614673557cbdb67704117314ac772d1e1760c0b","tid":1135253,"uid":19454,"like":143,"dislike":2,"score":141,"quote":{"pid":"f6552651e9948fdb9252ad4298da0d0eadc038a4","tid":1135253,"uid":152516,"like":855,"dislike":2,"score":853,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:51:32.000Z","msg":"會俾錢先係難以置信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:54:48.000Z","msg":"可能佢唸住 即刻賣樓 交款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0325e5d637a5b1b256702a9d12ae0d47c6a12edf","tid":1135253,"uid":118647,"like":15,"dislike":31,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⋯⋯咁大間pccw衰啲咁既野"},{"pid":"fb1b56eaa80609ec9b53ea839b71f139f8cec45b","tid":1135253,"uid":178875,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:58:57.000Z","msg":"推到上報唔知R到幾多賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2bee779a3adab903736b